SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE ORGANIZATION HAS BEEN CLASSIFIED AS AN ARIZONA NONPROFIT CORPORATION THAT IS EXEMPT FROM FEDERAL AND STATE INCOME TAXES UNDER SECTION 501(C)(3) OF THE INTERNAL REVENUE CODE; IN ADDITION, THE ORGANIZATION HAS NO UNRELATED BUSINESS INCOME TAX LIABILITIES. THEREFORE, NO PROVISION HAS BEEN MADE FOR INCOME TAXES DUE IN THE ACCOMPANYING FINANCIAL STATEMENTS. THE ORGANIZATIONS HAS ALSO BEEN CLASSIFIED AS AN ENTITY THAT IS NOT A PRIVATE FOUNDATION WITHIN THE MEANING OF SECTION 509(A) AND QUALIFIES FOR DEDUCTIBLE CONTRIBUTIONS AS PROVIDED IN SECTION 170(B)(1)(A)(VI).
